{"build_type":"library","description":"Return 1 if the NUL-terminated string `needle` occurs anywhere in the NUL-terminated string at `ptr`, else 0. Naive search: test string_has_prefix at the current position; if not, advance ptr by one and recurse (tail). Stops at the haystack's NUL. An empty needle matches (prefix of everything). O(n*m) — fine for .ipm-sized sources and short queries. Reuses string_has_prefix.","module_name":"verify-string-contains-target-substring","package_name":"verify-string-contains-target-substring","function_definitions":{"verify-string-contains-target-substring":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"ptr","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"needle","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"verify-string-starts-matching-prefix","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"ptr"},{"kind":"var","value":"needle"},{"kind":"var","value":"zero"}],"result_assignment_variable":"hp","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"hp"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"one"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"c","base":"ptr","index":"zero","scale":1},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"==","lhs":{"value":"c"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"ptr2","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"ptr2","lhs":{"value":"ptr"},"rhs":{"value":"one"}},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"verify-string-contains-target-substring","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"ptr2"},{"kind":"var","value":"needle"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}]}}}